Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.01,Mami,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.97,Mami,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就速战速决吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.68,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那个…
