Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.90,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:29.16,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉这家伙的…  是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.52,kaoju1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意Charlotte的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.63,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都捡回一条命了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.56,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这一幕烙印在眼中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.73,Homura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为魔法少女就是这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:52.95,Sayaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:59.42,Sayaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来  那是… 那个是…
